# Frontend — copy to `.env` or `.env.production` and set values before `npm run build`.
# Vite only exposes variables prefixed with VITE_.

# --- Azure App Service (FastAPI) API URL ---
# Set when the UI is NOT served from the same host as the API (e.g. SPA on Azure Storage
# static website, API on App Service). No trailing slash.
# Example: https://rsli-api.azurewebsites.net
VITE_API_ORIGIN=

# --- Optional: public URL of this SPA (Azure Storage static website) ---
# Not read by app code today; use for your own scripts / documentation / future features.
# Example: https://yourstorage.z20.web.core.windows.net
# VITE_AZURE_STORAGE_STATIC_ORIGIN=
